# Snapshot: examples/04_procs

### Source: `examples/04_procs.frog`

```frog
proc inc int -- int do 1 + end
proc dec int -- int do 1 - end
proc good int -- bool do 5 > end
proc show int -- int do ? dup print end

proc main -- do
    10
    while dup good do
      dec
      show
    end
    drop
end
```

### Run

Command:

```text
py -m frog run examples/04_procs.frog
```

